Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.50,1:16:27.06,ED,,0,1280,0,,{\fad(120,240)\blur0.6}Vous êtes le monde
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.66,1:16:32.94,ED,,0,1280,0,,{\fad(120,240)\blur0.6}Étoile, et toi
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.59,1:16:38.72,ED,,0,1280,0,,{\fad(120,240)\blur0.6}Et toi, et moi
Dialogue: 0,1:16:42.82,1:16:46.93,ED,,0,1280,0,,{\fad(120,240)\blur0.6}Tout ce que je vois
Dialogue: 0,1:16:48.82,1:16:52.88,ED,,0,1280,0,,{\fad(120,240)\blur0.6}Tout ce que je ressens
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.40,1:17:01.21,ED,,0,1280,0,,{\fad(120,240)\blur0.6}Tu es mon univers
